subs.text: The best campaign commercial ever. So simple. A nostalgic song, beautifully performed. Stock footage of American workers and families, esp in Vermont, interspersed with video from campaign events. These things aren't complicated. I bet Bernie and S&G would let Biden use the same format.
Call for feeds. I'm working on a bit of demo software and need a few blogroll-supporting feeds that have <source:blogroll> elements.
